WEBVTT

1
00:06:16.890 --> 00:06:18.150 
这定是个圈套
This has to be a setup.

2
00:06:18.170 --> 00:06:20.510 
你们继续寻找老板无罪的证据
You guys work on finding proof the boss is innocent.

3
00:06:20.580 --> 00:06:22.700 
我要去给他创造点逃跑的时间
I'm gonna try to buy him some getaway time.

4
00:06:22.780 --> 00:06:23.450 
怎么做
How?

5
00:06:23.580 --> 00:06:25.830 
破坏搜捕行动
By sabotaging the pursuit.

6
00:06:26.420 --> 00:06:30.130 
女士 我自荐领头猎捕宝贝逃犯
Ma'am, I volunteer to head up the fugitive baby hunt.

7
00:06:30.290 --> 00:06:31.250 
你有什么资质
Qualifications?

8
00:06:31.350 --> 00:06:33.390 
有一次我在日托所
Well, this one time when I was in daycare,

9
00:06:33.490 --> 00:06:36.610 
教室里的乌龟不见了 大家都觉得它死了
the classroom turtle ran away, and everyone figured it was...

10
00:06:37.500 --> 00:06:39.220 
我就放弃了吗 没有
But did I give up? No!

11
00:06:39.370 --> 00:06:43.210 
我整整五天没合眼 它终于被我找到了
I didn't sleep for five days until I found that turtle!

12
00:06:43.880 --> 00:06:45.460 
然后让它付出了代价
And made him pay.

